content.rendered:
On the 16th of August Prestige Motorcars worked alongside with Aston Martin Jakarta in unveiling one of our latest #MysteriousNewStars.

This is a very special car. So special there is only one in Indonesia and limited to 175 units worldwide. It is the Aston Martin Vanquish S Ultimate.

With a roaring V12, full carbon fibre body and its extra sleek styling, this car is sure to turn heads on the street. 

Another factor that makes this car very special, is the fact that it is the las Aston Martin to use a naturally aspirated V12 engine, and what better to end the era with this limited, top of the line Vanquish model. 

We had a blast hosting this event with Aston Martin Jakarta. For those who could not make it to the event, stay tuned for the official coverage on on YouTube channel soon!
